* Dinobot growled, he had also heard Liono's transmission. If he had been a 
lesser bot he would have jumped for joy at the announcement of battle, but 
to do so would taint his honor and disgrace himself. He just smiled to 
himself and looked down at his claws, did he need another, more stronger 
weapon?
Dinobot thought that his new body was stronger then he really needed but he 
wasn't one to complain about that, but was it strong enough to ward off 3 
maybe even 4 Predacon attackers? He sighed, if it could then good for it but 
right now he had to conserve it's energy.
Dinobot looked at Tavatron and a smile played at the edges of his lips, he 
reached behind himself and pulled out a reround laser-pulse rifle, he had 
found it in the same room that Tavatron and himself were in only half a 
mega-cycle ago.
He slammed a load cartridge into the loading dock of the rifle and powered 
up the fusion pulse, he then looked at Tavatron...a sinister yet pleased 
look on his face.*

"You were saying?"
